{"tid":643424,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"加司機仇視女性　撞人前發「毒男革命」宣言","createTime":"2018-04-26T13:11:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-27T00:26:11.000Z","uid":25558,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"1b8fc18e935dbcab2a3ddd5e08b1e9c938af0790","tid":643424,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T13:11:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180426/20373289?_ga=2.75181970.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180426%2F20373289%3F_ga%3D2.75181970.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&d=U%2F7c%2BUS8Ziu8fUlWKI0m3JZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=84594e59\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180426%2F20373289%3F_ga%3D2.75181970.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&h=6c6d461d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180426/20373289?_ga=2.75181970.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年04月26日 <br />\n<br />\n加司機仇視女性　撞人前發「毒男革命」宣言<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180426/large/26wx7p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180426%2Flarge%2F26wx7p.jpg&h=55e50091&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n ■Ken Lam（左）與父親。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【車撞人群】<br />\n<br />\n加拿大多倫多周一的貨車撞人案，10名死者大部份是女性，警方調查發現疑犯在撞人前數分鐘曾在社交網貼出「毒男革命」宣言，相信他因社交障礙和仇視女性行兇，無關恐襲。<br />\n<br />\n前日被控10項一級謀殺罪及13項企圖謀殺罪的米納西安（Alek Minassian），曾在facebook貼出一段文字：「大兵呼叫軍士長4chan&hellip;&hellip;毒男革命已開始！讓我們推翻型男美女！大神羅杰萬歲！」<br />\n<br />\n羅杰（Elliot Rodger）是2014年在美國加州大學殺傷十多人後自殺的槍手，生前常在網上以「毒男/非自願獨身」身份抱怨「追女不遂」。米納西安在貼文自稱大兵，但加國國防部證實他在受訓16天後自行退役；4chan相信是「毒男」討論區代號。案發後其戶口前日被facebook管理員關掉。<br />\n<br />\n美聯社  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n特讚金正恩「可敬」被轟無視血腥暴政<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n擒兇警父親曾任港輔警"},{"pid":"efd07789e86d5622193d6d9d06830062290bad87","tid":643424,"uid":77569,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T13:17:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c0edd89d77f2b2e7ad936a4a65d8cc76bf168917","tid":643424,"uid":132587,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T13:18:08.000Z","msg":"好彩香港d毒撚車都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"060816098413779ebee832f52b8fbd7d0b3e1bbc","tid":643424,"uid":117332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T13:21:02.000Z","msg":"Facebook正垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"164cb9cedfce589e68634cf605e762e509c3c4a7","tid":643424,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T13:22:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be7139482188a8916d5cda3b30ada7fc2b3e3d59","tid":643424,"uid":143499,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T13:27:43.000Z","msg":"毒撚死淨把口: 懦弱、懦夫、怕事<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n毒撚作出實際行動: 變態、中二病、反社會<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n連登仔嘅logic根本同港女睇仔一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n連登仔又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47e3e96d79aa3951f41c47d539641671a9107048","tid":643424,"uid":76488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T13:28:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0d573ed99397be31752f31f78c1969f5dbcccb18","tid":643424,"uid":143499,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"47e3e96d79aa3951f41c47d539641671a9107048","tid":643424,"uid":76488,"like":0,"dislike":